filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT
    l4d2.user1 AS Player, SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' then 1 else 0 end) as Kills, SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.event = 'PlayerKilled' then 1 else 0 end) as Deaths, SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' then 1 else 0 end)/CASE WHEN (SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.event = 'PlayerKilled' then 1 else 0 end)) > 0 then SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.event = 'PlayerKilled' then 1.0 else 0 end) else 1.0 end  AS \"K/D Ratio\"
    FROM \"file*\" WHERE l4d2.user1 IS NOT NULL AND l4d2.user1 NOT IN ('Nick','Ellis','Francis','Bill','Coach','Rochelle','Zoey','Louis','(1)Nick','(1)Ellis','(1)Francis','(1)Bill','(1)Coach','(1)Rochelle','(1)Zoey','(1)Louis','Smoker','Jockey','Boomer','Charger','Hunter','Spitter','(1)Smoker','(1)Jockey','(1)Boomer','(1)Charger','(1)Hunter','(1)Spitter','Tank','SurvivorBot','entityflame','env_fire','infected','prop_door_rotating_checkpoint','prop_physics','trigger_hurt','trigger_hurt_ghost','witch','insect_swarm', 'env_explosion') GROUP BY l4d2.user1"
| table perPage=25 
  font={font align="left" color="#000000" family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" italic=false size=24 underline=false weight="normal"}
| render containerStyle={containerStyle}

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT
     l4d2.human_map AS Map, count(*)/2 as \"Play Count\", DATETIME_FORMAT(CAST(FIRST_VALUE(\"@timestamp\") as DATE), 'dd/MM/yyyy') as \"Last Played\", FIRST_VALUE(l4d2.map_size) as \"# of Levels in Map\"
    FROM \"file*\" WHERE l4d2.human_map IS NOT NULL Group by l4d2.human_map"
| table perPage=25 
  font={font align="left" color="#000000" family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" italic=false size=24 underline=false weight="normal"}

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT
    l4d2.user1 AS Player, SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' then 1 else 0 end) as \"Total Kills\", SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' and l4d2.user2 = 'infected' then 1 else 0 end) as \"Infected Kills\", SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' and l4d2.user2 != 'infected' then 1 else 0 end) as \"Player Kills\"
    FROM \"file*\" WHERE l4d2.user1 IS NOT NULL AND l4d2.user1 NOT IN ('Nick','Ellis','Francis','Bill','Coach','Rochelle','Zoey','Louis','(1)Nick','(1)Ellis','(1)Francis','(1)Bill','(1)Coach','(1)Rochelle','(1)Zoey','(1)Louis','Smoker','Jockey','Boomer','Charger','Hunter','Spitter','(1)Smoker','(1)Jockey','(1)Boomer','(1)Charger','(1)Hunter','(1)Spitter','Tank','SurvivorBot','entityflame','env_fire','infected','prop_door_rotating_checkpoint','prop_physics','trigger_hurt','trigger_hurt_ghost','witch','insect_swarm', 'env_explosion') GROUP BY l4d2.user1"

  query="SELECT

    SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' and l4d2.user2 = 'Farmer' then 1 else 0 end) as \"Killed Farmer\", 
    SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' and l4d2.user2 = 'Fedak' then 1 else 0 end) as \"Killed Fedak\",  
    SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' and l4d2.user2 = 'Mustack' then 1 else 0 end) as \"Killed Mustack\", 
    SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' and l4d2.user2 = 'Orunlu' then 1 else 0 end) as \"Killed Orunlu\", 
    SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' and l4d2.user2 = 'Randex' then 1 else 0 end) as \"Killed Randex\",
    SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' and l4d2.user2 = 'SgtBrockoli' then 1 else 0 end) as \"Killed SgtBrockoli\", 
    SUM(CASE WHEN l4d2.action = 'killed' and l4d2.user2 = 'Zuess4' then 1 else 0 end) as \"Killed Zuess4\",
